# mstack CI

## Approach

- Read **failure logs**; identify the **root** failure (first error, not cascading noise).
- Fix with the **smallest** change that restores green; match existing workflow style.

## Do not

- Comment out tests, remove linters, or `|| true` failures **without explicit user approval** (same spirit as `mstack-permissions.mdc`).
- Bump images or actions blindly — note **why** and pin when the repo pins.

## Secrets and env

- Never embed secrets in workflow YAML; use **secrets** / **vars** per platform conventions.

## After fix

- State what was run locally vs what CI will prove; suggest follow-up if flaky.
